import React from 'react'; import {useEffect} from 'react'; import {useState} from 'react'; import axios from 'axios'; import './nba.css' const Nba = () => { const [data, setData] = useState([]); const loadData = async () => { const response = await axios.get("http://localhost:3001/api/get/nbateams") setData(response.data); }; useEffect (() => { loadData(); }, []); return ( {data.map((item, index) => { return ( ) })}
